projectDesc.p: This TEI P5 document contains four transcription layers of Tibetan text: (1) Diplomatic: preserves original manuscript features from Transkribus (with page/line structure, facsimile coordinates) (2) Normalized: reading text with standardized orthography (3) Segmented: word-tokenized version with utterance boundaries (4) Annotated: linguistic analysis with POS (part-of-speech) tags
